account management function at fallon and served as the senior agency representative on ralston purina pet foods lee jeans macromedia and long john silvers he led the new business pitch for miller lite  one of fallons most significant and high profile wins during his tenure at fallon he served as group director for miller lite and ralston purina two of the agencys largest accounts from  to  and management supervisor on ralston from  to  mr stoddart served at leo burnett for  years as a media buyerplanner on hewlettpackard since  and a transition to account management to begin working on clients such as keebler tropicana and mcdonalds he served as vice president and account supervisor since  he served at mcdonalds youth business as an account director since  he has been an independent director at hasbro inc since march   he serves as director of carbon media group llc mr stoddart has led the push into branded entertainment at ford with the development of several brand integration programs and partnerships including “american idol“ ““ “extreme makeover home edition“ and “american dreams“ he serves as vice chair of american advertising federation inc and has been its director since june   while at ford mr stoddart was also a recipient of the prestigious american advertising federation “hall of fame“ achievement award in  recognizing advertising professionals under the age of  who have demonstrated outstanding career achievements with measurable results mr stoddart completed his bachelors in arts in american government at dartmouth college in read full background corporate headquarters  avenue des champsélyséesparis iledefrance francephone      fax  board members memberships directoroutdoor hub llcpresentvice chairamerican advertising federation incpresentindependent directorhasbro inc education ba dartmouth college other affiliations hasbro incleo burnett company incdartmouth collegearc worldwide incamerican advertising federation incoutdoor hub llc annual compensation