 the chief executive officer of one of the largest advertising agencies mr stoddart is recognized for his leadership in the development and integration of shopper digital social and mobile capabilities as part of a companys overall marketing and brand strategy the board believes mr stoddart possesses knowledge expertise and experience regarding branding and brand building marketing strategy and marketing communications across media platforms including in traditional advertising digital advertising and social media expertise in media planning launching branded content and products and expertise in media trends and strategic planning for businesses building global contentdriven brands source hasbro inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view richard s stoddarts full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like richard s stoddart more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in richard s stoddarts network and community follow changes in richard s stoddarts employment and moneyinmotion connect with richard s stoddart through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example richard s stoddart richard s stoddarts connections  sign up now to view richard s stoddarts  connections » basil l anderson board member becton dickinson david d hargreaves former executive vice president and chief strategy officer hasbro inc alan r batkin board member cantel medical corp tracy a leinbach board member hasbro inc wiebe tinga executive vice president and chief commercial officer hasbro inc deborah m thomas executive vice president and chief financial officer hasbro inc alfred j verrecchia chairman of the board iron mountain incorporated alan g hassenfeld board member salesforce frank j biondi board member seagate technology plc edward m philip board member hasbro inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch exe